ur team with 70 unique creature (Fae's) for you to master! Each Fae has a unique set of abilities and elemental type. Setup ability combinations for fun and engaging strategies! </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The FaeTerra <strong>Demo</strong> offers Casual and Ranked matches battle with friends in PVP!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265220/extras/77a8815ab4cb59cb53158b76061ce573.avif?t=1761802156\" width=608 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265220/extras/e5c0379c2700ae9bb28f19d8890fc858.poster.avif?t=1761802156\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265220/extras/e5c0379c2700ae9bb28f19d8890fc858.webm?t=1761802156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265220/extras/e5c0379c2700ae9bb28f19d8890fc858.mp4?t=1761802156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Evolve</strong> your Fae's by combining Fae's of the same evolutionary line or using XP orbs.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FaeTerra Demo </strong>is all about discovering unique strategies and combos to create the most powerful build. You will be immersed with impactful decisions that creates a  fun chill deckbuilding experience!    </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265220/extras/c950ef266ea760aea1bbd58ceffd7eb2.avif?t=1761802156\" width=608 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265220/extras/ff6f64a04027035e99809b7675ce8f4c.poster.avif?t=1761802156\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265220/extras/ff6f64a04027035e99809b7675ce8f4c.webm?t=1761802156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265220/extras/ff6f64a04027035e99809b7675ce8f4c.mp4?t=1761802156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Custom builds</strong> allow player's to craft their very own unique team! Start by choosing (30) creatures you want in your build deck. Apply (1) creature (Fae) to your gold slot increasing the chance of roll/drawing this creature (Fae)!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Custom build packs for crafting and testing unique builds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 70 creatures to choose from in the <strong>FaeTerra Demo</strong>. All other Fae's will be locked.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
